-- Romney Requests Extension for Income Tax Filings, Campaign Says
-- B y   J o n a t h a n   S a l a n t
-- 2012-04-13T21:31:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-13/romney-requests-extension-for-income-tax-filings-campaign-says.html
Republican presidential candidate
 Mitt Romney  today requested a six-month extension to file his
2011 federal income taxes, said Andrea Saul, his campaign
spokeswoman. Saul said he would file his taxes and release the
return before the Nov. 6 general election.  To contact the reporter on this story:
